Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.91,0:01:34.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘉依卡
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.37,0:01:37.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.61,0:01:40.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事 問題無
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.08,0:01:43.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我們的嘉依卡怎樣了?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.25,0:01:44.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.82,0:01:46.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,當然
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.93,0:01:49.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很好 那趕緊開始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.29,0:01:51.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 開始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.11,0:01:55.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,順便一提 若交換人質時我們遭到狙擊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.60,0:01:57.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或踩到陷阱 我就會拉動這根繩子
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.60,0:02:01.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它會引燃炸藥 炸飛我們週遭一帶
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.24,0:02:02.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.91,0:02:05.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哼 故弄玄虛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.24,0:02:08.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那豈不是你們也得同歸於盡…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.07,0:02:09.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這就是亂破師的戰法
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.36,0:02:17.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是想保證首先人質成功交換 其它容後再說
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.17,0:02:19.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.69,0:02:22.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對方也是毫不疏忽啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.85,0:02:23.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還挺棘手的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.56,0:02:26.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去吧 小姑娘
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.40,0:02:30.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去吧

Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.84,0:02:43.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,紅與白

Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.83,0:02:55.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難道…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.22,0:02:59.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奇眼鳥
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.30,0:03:01.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這數量可麻煩了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.02,0:03:11.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂喂喂 怎麼回事?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.39,0:03:13.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你還好吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.95,0:03:19.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這幫傢伙應該沒有結群的習性
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.61,0:03:20.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被操縱了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.07,0:03:21.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恐怕是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.20,0:03:28.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,魚自己跳到地上?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.40,0:03:33.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我互換了在水中與空氣中的感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.45,0:03:38.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,若多項知覺失常 任何生物都不能安然無恙
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.11,0:03:43.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這招的好處在於 不用擔心因魔法本身而誤殺對方
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.77,0:03:46.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正適合用於活捉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.43,0:03:48.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過 真是令我吃了一驚
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.58,0:03:50.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒想到來了兩個嘉依卡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.24,0:03:53.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,求之不得的機會
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.58,0:03:57.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全都抓回去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.73,0:04:05.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小心
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.85,0:04:07.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,碰到光線就完了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.69,0:04:08.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要回頭 快點跑
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.38,0:04:18.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用魔法遮掩視線嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.47,0:04:20.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我們也動手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.33,0:04:25.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,混蛋 不還是虛張聲勢嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.46,0:04:29.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 這次有人礙事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.19,0:04:31.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,交換暫時中止吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.26,0:04:33.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.52,0:04:34.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然如此
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.70,0:04:35.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,此地 不宜久留
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.15,0:04:42.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去追那邊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.43,0:04:43.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.57,0:04:45.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這種時候 魔法真是方便
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.34,0:04:47.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們只能殺出去了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.50,0:04:49.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.34,0:04:50.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,武器 返還
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.10,0:04:52.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我 戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.13,0:04:56.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兄長
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.10,0:04:58.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,眼下挨過此劫為先
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.03,0:04:59.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.20,0:05:02.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感謝
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.38,0:05:50.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦? 你們怎麼了?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.89,0:05:54.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像很累的樣子?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.86,0:05:55.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.08,0:06:00.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘉依卡 你換了髮型?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.24,0:06:03.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你呀…這傢伙看起像平常的嘉依卡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.48,0:06:06.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是嗎 那是誰?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.12,0:06:09.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呃 雖然也是嘉依卡啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.37,0:06:11.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總之 以後再和你說
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.31,0:06:14.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,目前 問題是這個
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.59,0:06:16.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但兄長 即使挪開了瓦礫
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.35,0:06:18.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們中也沒有能駕駛的人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.19,0:06:20.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是說啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.24,0:06:22.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而再磨蹭下去就要被追上了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.25,0:06:24.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只能丟在這裡了呀…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.19,0:06:26.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼 要開動這機車?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.25,0:06:28.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要我幫你開嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.87,0:06:30.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我能用魔法的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.83,0:06:31.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你來?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.85,0:06:33.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要你願意之後和我打一場
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.32,0:06:36.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了 趕緊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.37,0:06:37.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,OK
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.58,0:06:49.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,裝鎧龍
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.53,0:06:58.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣根本無從追跡…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.32,0:07:05.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,馬特烏斯先生
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.55,0:07:06.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我失手了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.83,0:07:10.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒想到這麼多棄獸竟能全部殺光
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.01,0:07:11.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是失算了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.84,0:07:15.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我這邊也是 所有線索都被破壞了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.40,0:07:20.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看來單靠我們兩人同時抓捕兩組嘉依卡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.38,0:07:21.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,終究是太托大了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.15,0:07:24.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兩名嘉依卡聚在一起究竟是想做什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.59,0:07:28.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過她們中是否有真身都還是未知之數
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.97,0:07:32.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或許反過來 其實都是真的?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.62,0:07:34.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在說什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.05,0:07:38.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然是皇帝 那妻妾如雲一點都不奇怪吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.12,0:07:41.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或許他為了萬無一失地培養出繼承人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.43,0:07:45.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,給生下來的所有女兒都取了嘉依卡這個名字…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.19,0:07:49.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你說所有的嘉依卡都是真的?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.18,0:07:50.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼會…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.74,0:07:55.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說到底我們對嘉依卡一無所知
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.60,0:07:57.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也許吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.18,0:08:01.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那更應該全都抓獲進行尋問了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.53,0:08:06.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在我們只能寄希望於前往佩利梅拉爾的本隊了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.77,0:08:16.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂喂 繞路走
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.14,0:08:21.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,六國會議期間 此路禁止通行
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.79,0:08:25.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,關於此前大戰中
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.15,0:08:30.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,迫降於加瓦爾尼公爵領的航天要塞索厄拉…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.64,0:08:36.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,據悉公爵動用了大量的化石思念料 擅自將要塞起動了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.83,0:08:38.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,目的不明
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.87,0:08:42.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,需立即遣使者問明公爵真意
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.97,0:08:44.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太過溫和!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.83,0:08:48.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟將處於聯合國管理下的航天要塞私有化
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.80,0:08:50.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反意昭然若揭
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.02,0:08:54.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對待逆賊 唯有以武力肅清!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.14,0:08:55.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莫急莫急
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.68,0:08:59.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,首先還是探探對方的態度吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.68,0:09:00.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比起此事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.88,0:09:06.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最近我國農民圍繞農地劃分問題紛爭不斷
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.68,0:09:09.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還請借助聯軍之力 予以鎮壓…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.41,0:09:10.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,農民的小衝突算什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.08,0:09:11.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比起這種問題
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.35,0:09:13.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還是先處理下在我國橫行霸道的強盜團夥…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.42,0:09:15.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不不 我國的貧窮問題…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.54,0:09:16.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肅靜
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.96,0:09:20.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請舉手後再發言
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.03,0:09:25.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有何事? 斯坦梅茨大人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.03,0:09:30.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,關於我克里曼機關正追蹤調查的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.44,0:09:32.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「棺姬嘉依卡」一事…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.78,0:09:34.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又是嘉依卡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.85,0:09:38.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這種民間傳說的報告 聽了純屬浪費時間
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.05,0:09:44.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 現在追蹤的嘉依卡 實際入手了數樣遺體
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.46,0:09:46.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其為真身的可信度…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.08,0:09:46.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,笑掉大牙
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.93,0:09:48.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比起這種天方夜譚
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.34,0:09:52.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你還不如去調停下方才講到的農民衝突
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.91,0:09:55.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這才是戰後復興機關的分內之事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.01,0:10:00.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,確實 此事想來正適合克里曼機關出面
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.40,0:10:02.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,諸位怎看?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.78,0:10:07.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,若命令如此…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.00,0:10:11.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼? 去鎮壓農村?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.71,0:10:14.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但根據馬特烏斯的報告
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.03,0:10:17.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘉依卡一行人已近在咫尺
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.95,0:10:19.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都到了這一步 怎可輕易…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.37,0:10:20.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的心情我可以理解
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.13,0:10:23.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但六國會議的決定不容違逆
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.43,0:10:25.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請立刻動身吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.91,0:10:29.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,遵命
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.17,0:10:33.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.36,0:11:01.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你 亂破師?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.30,0:11:01.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.39,0:11:03.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.47,0:11:06.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,僱主 我的假貨?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.11,0:11:10.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我說過 現在誰真誰假還說不准呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.07,0:11:13.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,報酬金額 提出
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.29,0:11:15.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,更多 我支付
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.76,0:11:18.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,遲早復興 賈茲帝國
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.53,0:11:20.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,報酬 如你所願
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.80,0:11:22.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要我為金錢而叛主?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.77,0:11:27.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒錯 亂破師為了金錢 可以受僱於任何勢力
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.76,0:11:29.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.94,0:11:32.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一旦選定了僱主就絕不會背叛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.43,0:11:35.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是我們唯一的驕傲
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.67,0:11:38.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.11,0:11:40.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,使命 絕對
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.44,0:11:42.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即使耗費一生
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.64,0:11:44.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也要努力完成
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.56,0:11:49.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有戰場戰鬥才是亂破師
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.08,0:11:52.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不止是為了錢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.61,0:11:55.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我 戰場 提供 可能
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.21,0:11:57.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能當你的主人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.62,0:11:58.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 我說過…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.67,0:12:00.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我 力量 需要
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.67,0:12:02.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戰鬥 奪回
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.56,0:12:03.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,路之所往 戰場
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.28,0:12:05.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,迷茫 搖擺 沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.34,0:12:13.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,該準備做飯了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.88,0:12:15.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,考慮 提議
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.80,0:12:16.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 我會考慮的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.53,0:12:43.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姑娘
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.62,0:12:45.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要買件武器嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.27,0:12:47.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我這品種齊全哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.32,0:12:50.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就知道能遇上你們
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.88,0:12:54.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,畢竟這附近只有這一個大城市
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.72,0:12:57.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘉依卡平安無事吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.52,0:12:58.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放心
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.17,0:13:01.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們也有人質在你那兒呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.92,0:13:10.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在猶豫?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.31,0:13:12.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,猶豫什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.36,0:13:15.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,猶豫追隨哪邊的嘉依卡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.64,0:13:16.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你聽到了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.16,0:13:19.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,托魯啊 你以前說過
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.53,0:13:23.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,實現重要之人的目的 就是自己的目的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.84,0:13:25.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那指的是嘉依卡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.33,0:13:27.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.33,0:13:30.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是渴望戰鬥所以才受僱於嘉依卡吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.90,0:13:34.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那轉到紅嘉依卡那邊不也一樣?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.98,0:13:37.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,仔細想想 其實投靠紅嘉依卡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.61,0:13:40.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,托魯更能盡情戰鬥吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.94,0:13:41.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你這麼想?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.18,0:13:42.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.47,0:13:45.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.72,0:13:46.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 阿卡莉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.73,0:13:49.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我回來了 兄長
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.75,0:13:51.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 有收獲嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.57,0:13:54.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有 交換的安排定下了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.12,0:13:58.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天黃昏 佩利梅拉爾中央廣場
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.78,0:14:00.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.03,0:14:02.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也去告知她
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.51,0:14:06.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,托魯會選哪邊呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.90,0:14:14.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,時間地點談好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.91,0:14:17.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你馬上可以回到那倆亂破師身邊了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.63,0:14:19.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感謝
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.91,0:14:21.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,唔 反倒被感謝…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.75,0:14:32.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,提議
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.43,0:14:36.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,提議 考慮 換主
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.22,0:14:37.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.63,0:14:41.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對我 不滿?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.07,0:14:45.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有不滿 復興帝國和復仇
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.11,0:14:48.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想必在目標明確的你的麾下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.96,0:14:51.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我更能盡情地戰鬥吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.42,0:14:53.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼 為什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.24,0:14:55.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你很強啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.45,0:14:58.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,無論精神還是肉體
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.42,0:15:01.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 那傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.85,0:15:04.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卻是個爛好人 全身上下都是可乘之隙
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.93,0:15:06.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且還老實又固執
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.81,0:15:08.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,令人放心不下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.42,0:15:11.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然都是被需要
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.28,0:15:15.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想效力於更需要我的一方
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.23,0:15:18.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就這麼回事啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.64,0:15:20.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再見
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.49,0:15:23.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我又何嘗不…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.63,0:15:28.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吶 去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.36,0:15:31.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再見 大叔
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.03,0:15:34.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不叫大叔 叫達比特
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.81,0:15:35.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,達比特
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.70,0:15:47.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.48,0:16:05.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,托魯 阿卡莉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.20,0:16:06.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.96,0:16:08.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.25,0:16:11.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.42,0:16:14.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,托魯 反應淡薄
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.04,0:16:17.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難不成我還得喜極而泣?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.87,0:16:19.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你饒了我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.29,0:16:21.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.61,0:16:24.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這時最為鬆懈
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.47,0:16:29.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,托魯其實挺擔心嘉依卡的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.47,0:16:31.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,詳細希望
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.84,0:16:34.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他保養武器保養個不停
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.62,0:16:37.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道的 托魯總是不坦率嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.94,0:16:40.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼說來著 怕羞?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.52,0:16:42.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,理解 大大理解
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.69,0:16:45.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 模仿就不能把口吻也模仿了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.12,0:16:49.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是阿卡莉的說話方式太難了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.62,0:16:55.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,致盲者 顯現
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.52,0:17:16.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.91,0:17:18.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剛才那是什麼? 魔法?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.77,0:17:19.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是那邊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.04,0:17:20.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,趁現在 我們走
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.33,0:17:21.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.03,0:17:24.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,賽爾瑪那傢伙 失敗了嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.12,0:17:26.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.92,0:17:30.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小嘉依卡 你不會被人家迷住了吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.50,0:17:34.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,粗俗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.05,0:17:45.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,趕快離開這裡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.82,0:17:48.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉嘉依卡 還得請你馬上去開車
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.97,0:17:52.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,結果托魯還是選了白嘉依卡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.24,0:17:55.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人類真有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.04,0:17:57.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說明 請求
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.46,0:17:58.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.50,0:18:00.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是那啥 怕羞啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.94,0:18:02.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怕羞你個頭
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.54,0:18:05.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘉依卡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.21,0:18:07.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿卡莉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.63,0:18:17.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿卡莉 感謝
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.64,0:18:21.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,歡迎回來 嘉依卡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.01,0:18:29.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,托魯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.30,0:18:31.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.61,0:18:34.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我 嘉依卡·托勒龐特
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.69,0:18:37.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘉依卡 有許多
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.68,0:18:39.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,似乎是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.66,0:18:43.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我 記憶 缺落
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.09,0:18:45.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,假貨 可能性…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.48,0:18:47.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就是你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.37,0:18:50.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我最初遇到的嘉依卡是你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.19,0:18:53.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想侍奉的嘉依卡也是你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.59,0:18:55.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這不就夠了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.23,0:19:03.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以 我會毫不猶豫地掃清你前路的一切障礙
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.10,0:19:07.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,無論對方是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.37,0:19:18.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我重申一次
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.29,0:19:20.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,交出遺體
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.88,0:19:21.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,休想
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.16,0:19:22.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,另外呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.28,0:19:26.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知為何 咱們的大小姐對你是青睞有加
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.74,0:19:31.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,若你帶著遺體加入我們
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.95,0:19:33.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就可以避免無用的爭鬥喔
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.86,0:19:37.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再加上你妹妹 聽說還有頭裝鎧龍?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.46,0:19:40.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她說一起來也沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.67,0:19:43.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,若照做 我這邊的公主 你們打算如何處置?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.29,0:19:47.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘉依卡 不需兩人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.83,0:19:49.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.62,0:19:51.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.31,0:19:52.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就是你們的敵人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.48,0:20:08.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,開膛者 顯現
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.95,0:20:21.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,托魯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.11,0:20:23.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,托魯不要動
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.62,0:20:28.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,閃爍者 顯現吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.73,0:20:29.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,The Flasher
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.29,0:20:37.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,障眼法嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.57,0:20:39.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我為鋼也
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.48,0:20:43.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鋼故不怯 鋼故不惑
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.29,0:20:47.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一旦逢敵 盡無一切躊躇
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.93,0:20:49.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為滅此兇器也
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.31,0:20:51.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鐵血轉化
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.44,0:21:09.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兄長
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.43,0:21:09.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他們呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.47,0:21:11.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不成 被逃了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.51,0:21:13.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,魔法師那邊呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.74,0:21:14.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我這邊也是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.85,0:21:16.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,托魯 阿卡莉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.68,0:21:19.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事? 兩人沒問題?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.46,0:21:28.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能這樣下去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.40,0:21:32.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不僅有人妨礙收集遺體
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.30,0:21:36.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,甚至還有人想搶奪我們收集的遺體
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.14,0:21:38.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下來該怎麼走…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.01,0:21:39.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,得好好想一想了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.04,0:21:47.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘉依卡 複數 不需
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.43,0:21:49.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,遲早 做了結
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.29,0:21:53.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宿命
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.69,0:23:28.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可怕山谷 訪問者 無人歸來
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.62,0:23:31.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或某處 遺體存在?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.96,0:23:35.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因此必須訪問 絕對生還
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.10,0:23:38.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下周 第七集 「不歸谷」

