Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.94,0:00:48.53,OPEDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\be2\bord2}戀愛笨蛋 看不清眼前
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.89,0:00:52.71,OPEDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\be2\bord2}束手無策 在這深夜裡
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.01,0:00:56.71,OPEDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\be2\bord2}走投無路 遵守著約定
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.04,0:01:02.30,OPEDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\be2\bord2}在自己鏡中留下投影
